description: The index reflects the returns that are potentially available through an unleveraged investment in the futures contracts on industrial metal commodities. It is currently composed of four futures contracts on industrial metals, three of which are traded on the London Metal Exchange and the other of which is traded on the COMEX division of the New York Mercantile Exchange and is a sub-index of the Dow Jones-UBS Commodity Index Total ReturnService Mark.
name: iPath Bloomberg Industrial Metals Subindex Total Return(SM) ETN
